summary.en: This trendy pair of denim jeans by Cotton On is a must-have in your bottom wear collection. The fresh colour and ripped detail uplift the look of these pants. Tailor-made from breathable fabric, this piece is skin-comforting and provides a snug fit. Furthermore, these jeans feature a button closure across the waist and slip-in pockets.
